Not everything made by gnomes is full of grease, gears and things that go "whirrr ping!". These active wee folk also have 6 unique robes that they can tailor that can be worn by any and all INT casters of all races.<p>
Gnomes receive their no drop oxidized robe pattern by telling Tesil Gludien (found in Ak'Anon at 1194, -720) "I need a robe pattern". Folks illusioned into gnomes will not be able to receive the pattern - these robes are meant to be made by gnomes and only gnomes.<br><div align="right">Last Modified By: EQTC Editor Krazick&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>

		Last Modified on: 2003-05-20 08:51:55&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></div><br>
